NG0423:3227: rang rig nyams su len pa ni //
NG0423:3228: ye shes rang bzhin 'gag med la //
NG0423:3229: rang snang rang shar gzung 'dzin bral //
NG0423:3230: me long gzugs brnyan ltar du sprad //
NG0423:3231: rtog pas nyams su blang pa ni //
NG0423:3232: bya bral lhun rdzogs gshog rgyangs 'dra //
NG0423:3233: rang rig rang gsal ngang la gnas //
NG0423:3234: dgongs pa ye shes nyams len ni //
NG0423:3235: dper na chu bo gad+ga bzhin //
NG0423:3236: rgyun gyi ngang la nyams su blang *//
NG0423:3238: 'bras bu la zlos nyams len ni //
NG0423:3239: nyi ma'i 'od zer shar ba bzhin //
NG0423:3240: sku gsum 'bral med ngang la blang *//
NG0423:3241: rnal 'byor lam gyi nyams len ni //
NG0423:3242: shes rab chen po don las ni //
NG0423:3244: dgongs pa ma yengs nyams su blang *//
NG0423:3245: rnal 'byor lus kyi nyams blang ba //
NG0423:3246: dang por dben par sems gzung nas //
NG0423:3247: rtogs nas rig pa'i rtsal sbyang ste //
NG0423:3248: nges shes rtogs pa shar na gnyis med spyod pa bya //
NG0423:3249: zhes seng ge sgra dgongs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0423:3250: nyams su long zhig par gdams pa'i le'u ste don gcig pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3251: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / nyams su blang ba'i gang zag rnams //
NG0423:3252: cig car rtogs sam rim gyis bgrod //
NG0423:3254: rtsol bas grub bam btsal med shar //
NG0423:3256: a ti cig car rtogs pa'i dgongs pa yang *//
NG0423:3257: yin don cig car rig pa'i don //
NG0423:3258: go rtogs dus grol dus su rim gyis dpyad //
NG0423:3259: dbang po bag chags lus 'di gcud la sgril //
NG0423:3260: dbang po rang yan bkug pas rtogs grol bde ba lus la 'char //
NG0423:3261: bar du gsengs la shes rig ngang la gcu //
NG0423:3262: de lus ngag gi byin rlabs nus pa skyes //
NG0423:3263: tha ma shes pa glod la 'gyu ba rang yan gtang *//
NG0423:3265: gzung 'dzin gcud la bor bas rig pa rang gsal 'char //
NG0423:3266: shar ba'i tshe na lhag de rang dgar mthong *//
NG0423:3267: lhag ge sa le ngang la 'bral med bya //
NG0423:3268: 'di ni ye shes rang yan bde ba chen po'i klong *//
NG0423:3269: rang byung ye shes chos su gzhi bzhengs la //
NG0423:3270: lta ba rtogs pas 'di la ci zhig lta //
NG0423:3271: rig pa 'od gsal lam du shar ba la //
NG0423:3272: sgom pa'i sems 'dzin 'di la ci zhig sgom //
NG0423:3273: kun tu bzang po dogs pa med dbyings la //
NG0423:3274: rig pa'i rgyal po'i ngang la rang grol thabs //
NG0423:3275: spyod pa dka' thub 'di la ci zhig bya //
NG0423:3276: snying po sku gsum lhun grub rang chas khyab //
NG0423:3277: rtsol bas bgrod nas 'bras bu ci zhig tshol //
NG0423:3278: dgongs pas mtshan ma rang grol te //
NG0423:3279: nyams la dus mi 'gyur yang snang ba 'gyur //
NG0423:3280: bde chen ye shes shar ba'i drod tshad yin //
NG0423:3281: chos sku ye shes sgo lnga rang shar la //
NG0423:3282: snang ba ngo bor dag pas rtsal snang rang grol lo //
NG0423:3283: dgongs pa rang la shar bas shes rab rgyun //
NG0423:3284: bag chags bag la zha bas sgrib med lung *//
NG0423:3285: snang ba rnam dag gzhi snang chen po la //
NG0423:3286: rang byung sku gsum byas pa'i chos ma yin //
NG0423:3288: 'od gsal sgrib med rtog pa med //
NG0423:3290: la rdzogs pas 'bras bu rtsol ba med //
NG0423:3291: snying po nang gsal chos sku'i snang ba la //
NG0423:3292: sgo lnga 'od gsal longs sku yul snang ngo *//
NG0423:3293: sprul pa'i snang ba ye shes zang thal te //
NG0423:3294: shar ba thams cad sgrib med ye shes bkrag / snang ba thams cad dngos med 'od gsal gdangs //
NG0423:3295: nyams len thams cad ma bcos 'od gsal ngang *//
NG0423:3296: rtog pa thams cad zang thal nam mkha'i mtha' //
NG0423:3297: lus ngag spyod pa rang shugs bar snang rlung *//
NG0423:3298: yon tan thams cad ma btsal rgya mtsho'i rlabs //
NG0423:3299: 'bras bu sgrub med ye shes nyi ma'i dkyil //
NG0423:3300: 'khor ba rang grol byang chub rin chen gling *//
NG0423:3301: rtogs ldan don la ji ltar spyad kyang snying po'i don //
NG0423:3302: 'khor 'das thams cad chos sku 'gag med rtsal //
NG0423:3303: 'on kyang gzung 'dzin rtag par lta bas 'khor bar 'ching *//
NG0423:3305: dgongs pa bca' ba'i le'u ste don gnyis pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3306: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag /
NG0423:3307: dus bzhi mnyam par ji ltar sbyar //
NG0423:3309: rig pa lta bu bag chags sbubs na gsal dus su //
NG0423:3310: chos sku bag chags sbubs na 'thums zhes bya //
NG0423:3311: longs sku tsit+ta dpal be'u'i nang gsal ba //
NG0423:3312: sprul sku 'dod pa'i sgo gsum rang grol yang *//
NG0423:3313: sku gsum gdangs kyi 'od gsal sgo lngar zang thal shar //
NG0423:3314: shar ba gsal ba ngo ma shes pas sgrib pa byung *//
NG0423:3316: zang thal ngo ma shes pas rtog par bzung *//
NG0423:3317: rang grol ngo ma shes pas sdug bsngal rgyud la bsags //
NG0423:3318: snying po ye shes gsal ba'i gnad kyis sgrib pa med //
NG0423:3319: thugs kyi rtsal rdzogs snang ba zang thal 'khrul pa med //
NG0423:3320: sku yi rtsal rdzogs longs sku ngo bor shar //
NG0423:3321: rang grol 'od gsal shar bas sdug bsngal gdung ba grol //
NG0423:3322: ngo bo 'gyur med chos sku rang sa zin //
NG0423:3324: 'od gsal rang la shar bas sgrib pa yongs su
NG0423:3325: dag / de yi dus su dus bzhi mnyam par
NG0423:3327: dbang po gnas sdud phyi sgo gcad pa'i dus //
NG0423:3328: de mtshon rang grol rang rig rtogs //
NG0423:3329: shes bya bum 'jug ye shes nang gsal dus //
NG0423:3330: bying rmugs gti mug ye shes ngang la bzla //
NG0423:3331: rig pa rang gsal ye shes nang sgo 'byed pa'i dus //
NG0423:3332: ye shes rang snang rang rtsal phyal bar mi gtong ba //
NG0423:3333: snang ba rgya yan rtogs gsal zang thal dus //
NG0423:3334: 'khrul rtog ye shes ngo bor shar bas zhen pa'i skyon yang bsal //
NG0423:3335: nyin mtshan kha sbyor chu bo rgyan gyi gnas //
NG0423:3336: 'khrul pa gzung 'dzin ngo bor mtha' grol ba'o //
NG0423:3337: mtshan mo gti mug yid lus la //
NG0423:3339: mthong snang rig byed rang snang rang grol gces //
NG0423:3340: de don ma rtogs ri dwags smig rgyu 'ded pa 'dra //
NG0423:3341: 'khrul pa da lta sha khrag lus 'di la //
NG0423:3342: ye shes rang shar snang ba rang grol gces //
NG0423:3343: de don ma rtogs rtog ge chos rnams spyod pa ni //
NG0423:3345: 'dab rdzab bsnan dang 'dra ste skam dus med //
NG0423:3346: bar du 'od gsal lus la ni //
NG0423:3347: 'od gsal rtogs pa'i gzer med na //
NG0423:3348: dmus long thang la gcod pa 'dra //
NG0423:3349: bag chags le lo thibs non nas //
NG0423:3350: phyin pa'i yul med srid pa'i bar dor 'khyams par 'gyur //
NG0423:3351: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa las /
NG0423:3352: dus bzhi mnyam par dgongs pa sbyor ba'i le'u ste don gsum pa'o ///
NG0423:3354: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / dgongs pa dus bzhi mnyam par sbyar byas nas //
NG0423:3355: dgongs pa nyams kyi drod rtags ji ltar 'byung *//
NG0423:3357: rnal 'byor sku gsum ji ltar yid ches nga *//
NG0423:3358: sems can dus na sangs rgyas dgongs par shar //
NG0423:3359: 'khor ba'i blo la 'khrul pa rang ngor log /
NG0423:3360: dus la 'gyu ba med kyang ye shes snang ba
NG0423:3361: 'char // 'khrul pa nga bdag snang ba ngo bor zad //
NG0423:3362: 'jig rten gnas kyang kun tu 'od kyi sa non te //
NG0423:3363: 'khrul pa'i sdug bsngal bde ba chen por grol //
NG0423:3364: mngon shes phra mo med kyang thams cad mkhyen pa'i shes rab shar //
NG0423:3365: 'khrul pa rang dag 'khor ba rgyun chad do //
NG0423:3366: der brda don sprad pas rang ngo shes //
NG0423:3367: 'gro don las la mtshams mi sbyor //
NG0423:3368: ma rig dbyings su dag nas mkhyen pa'i 'char sgo bye //
NG0423:3369: sku gsum snying po 'gyur med pas //
NG0423:3370: 'dzin rtog zang thal shar bas rdzu 'phrul mngon shes ldan //
NG0423:3371: phyi yi snang ba dag snang 'gro drug sgyu mar grol //
NG0423:3372: 'gro drug skye gnas 'khor ba'i sgo yang 'gags //
NG0423:3373: thugs rje 'od du gsal bas 'gyu byed rtog sgrib
NG0423:3374: dag / 'khor ba skye ba'i rkyen med mngon sangs
NG0423:3375: rgyas // chos sku rang ngo shes pas rtogs pa'i yul la shes rab shar //
NG0423:3376: ma rig rig par dag pas mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob //
NG0423:3377: thugs rje zer du 'phro bas rdzu 'phrul rtsal yang rdzogs //
NG0423:3378: longs sku rang la shar bas ye shes ngang la gsal //
NG0423:3379: thugs kyi rtsal rdzogs mkhyen pa gsum yang shar //
NG0423:3381: 'gag med gsung gi rtsal rdzogs chos rnams thogs med mkhyen //
NG0423:3382: rnal 'byor lam gyi drod tshad mtha' ru skyol //
NG0423:3384: rnal 'byor drod tshad bstan pa'i le'u ste don bzhi pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3385: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / nyams su blang dus ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3387: rnal 'byor nyams su len dus lnga //
NG0423:3388: da lta 'khrul ba'i snang ba la //
NG0423:3389: rang snang ye shes lam du bcar //
NG0423:3390: thun mong ting 'dzin gsal ba las //
NG0423:3391: ye shes rang shar lam du bcar //
NG0423:3392: rmi lam snang ba nying 'khrul la //
NG0423:3393: ye shes sgyu mas ye shes sgyu ma blta //
NG0423:3394: chos nyid bar do dag pa'i snang ba la //
NG0423:3395: sangs rgyas bden pa'i rang sa de ltar gzung *//
NG0423:3396: der mkhyen pa'i gsal ma thebs na //
NG0423:3397: blo dman srid pa'i bar dor ye shes spongs gdab bya //
NG0423:3398: rtogs pa tha ma skye ba rgyud las grol bar 'gyur //
NG0423:3399: ye shes rang snang lam du byed @#//
NG0423:3401: 'dug yang chos nyid gdangs las ma g.yos la //
NG0423:3402: 'gro yang ye shes rang gdangs rang snang ma 'gags te //
NG0423:3403: nyi ma mer ma rang snang gdangs dang chas nas 'gro ba bzhin //
NG0423:3404: nyal yang rig pa'i ngang las ma g.yos klong *//
NG0423:3405: nang nub rig pa zang thal rtsal gyi ngang la
NG0423:3406: 'dug / gzung 'dzin phra rags dngos med rang ngo
NG0423:3407: grol // mtshan ma rang sar grol ba ye shes rnal 'byor che //
NG0423:3408: spyod lam rnam bzhi ci spyad kyang *//
NG0423:3409: ye shes gdangs las mi 'da' zhing *//
NG0423:3410: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NG0423:3411: bya gar 'phur mkha' las mi 'da' ltar //
NG0423:3412: rtogs ldan rnal 'byor ngang las g.yos pa med //
NG0423:3413: ces seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa las /
NG0423:3414: rnal 'byor nyams myong dus bstan pa'i le'u ste don lnga pa'o ///
NG0423:3416: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / rnal 'byor lam gyi rnam gzhag tu //
NG0423:3417: sku gsum dang po ye shes rtsal du gang las byung *//
NG0423:3418: gnas dang grol ba'i rim pa ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3420: thog ma rang rig chos sku ngo bo las //
NG0423:3421: ye shes rtsal lnga thog ma gang las shar //
NG0423:3422: 'di nyid rigs kyi bu yis nges par zung *//
NG0423:3423: shes rab rtsal ni ma btsal rang shar te //
NG0423:3424: dang po byung yang sku gsum rtsal las byung *//
NG0423:3425: bar du gnas yang shes rab rtsal la gnas //
NG0423:3426: tha ma grol yang 'dus thim sku gsum ngang du grol //
NG0423:3427: ma btsal rang shar lnga nyid bshad pa ni //
NG0423:3429: rig pa chos nyid stong pa dang *//
NG0423:3430: de nyid 'gag pa med pa dang *//
NG0423:3431: de gnyis dbye ba med pa dang *//
NG0423:3432: de ltar shes pa'i shes rab dang *//
NG0423:3433: de las thogs med 'od zer lnga //
NG0423:3434: de lnga mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga shar ro //
NG0423:3435: ye shes lnga ni 'od lngar shar ba yin //
NG0423:3436: 'od lnga rigs lnga longs sku lngar shar ro //
NG0423:3437: rigs lnga dbyings la yum lnga ma 'gags shar //
NG0423:3438: yab yum sems dpa' sems ma ma 'gags te //
NG0423:3439: sems dpa' sems ma dbang po ma 'gags pa //
NG0423:3440: de ni ye shes rang shar dgongs pa'o //
NG0423:3441: rang shar rang snang gzhan snang rtog pa de la med //
NG0423:3443: de ltar 'byung lnga phung po sgo lnga dang *//
NG0423:3444: rig pa 'od gsal dbyer med rtsal gyi gdangs las shar //
NG0423:3445: de nyid ye shes gdangs su rtogs pa ni //
NG0423:3446: bla mas gdams ngag rkyen gyis snang bas na //
NG0423:3447: 'od kyang don shes gnas 'gyur ma yin te //
NG0423:3448: dper na khang khyim nang gi nam mkha' ni //
NG0423:3449: sgrib byed ra bas bcad gyur kyang *//
NG0423:3450: mthongs kyi nang na zang thal nam mkha' dbyer med do //
NG0423:3451: de bzhin sems can bag chags sbubs kyis bcad mod kyang *//
NG0423:3452: don gyi ye shes sgo lnga zang thal shar //
NG0423:3453: rtog pa'i ye shes sgrib med zang thal lo //
NG0423:3454: de phyir rnal 'byor sku gsum yin pa'i ngang las bdag med do //
NG0423:3455: de yi ngang la dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad bzhugs //
NG0423:3456: 'byed med gsal ba shes rab rtogs pa med //
NG0423:3459: stong nyid rdo rje lta bu'i sku thob pa //
NG0423:3460: longs sku de las 'gag med thugs rje shar //
NG0423:3461: sprul sku thugs rje ye shes dbyings kyi mngal sdud ces //
NG0423:3462: seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0423:3463: thog ma ye shes kyi rtsal gang las byung ba dang */
NG0423:3464: bar du sangs rgyas sems can ji ltar gnas pa'i le'u ste don drug pa'o ///
NG0423:3466: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / dang po byung yang ye shes rtsal las byung *//
NG0423:3467: tha ma ye shes dbyings su ji ltar sdud ce na //
NG0423:3469: longs snang sprul pa'i zhing khams 'gro drug nas //
NG0423:3470: 'dod pa'i yon tan yul lnga yang *//
NG0423:3471: sgo lnga dbang po lnga yi ngang du grol //
NG0423:3472: sems dpa' sems ma sgo lnga de //
NG0423:3473: sku lnga phung po lnga dang yul lnga 'byung ba lnga la grol //
NG0423:3474: rigs lnga 'od lnga ye shes lnga yi ngang du grol //
NG0423:3475: ye shes lnga yang rig pa'i mtshan nyid lnga yi ngang du grol //
NG0423:3476: mtshan nyid lnga yang 'dzin med rig pa'i 'od la grol //
NG0423:3477: de la dbang po gnas sdud dgongs pa zhes su gsungs //
NG0423:3478: de las grol nas ngang la ma g.yos pa //
NG0423:3479: chos nyid chos sku dbyer med bum pas bya //
NG0423:3480: ye shes rang rig mar me lta bus gsal //
NG0423:3481: de la shes bya bum 'jug dgongs pa zhes su bya //
NG0423:3482: thams cad byung yang sku gsum rang las byung *//
NG0423:3483: thams cad snang yang rang snang thim pa rang la grol //
NG0423:3484: thams cad gsal ba rang gsal ngo bor mched //
NG0423:3485: thim dang grol ba ye shes ngang du sdud //
NG0423:3486: dper na nam mkha' sprin dang khu rlang ci byung yang *//
NG0423:3487: nam mkha'i ngang byung gnas thim nam mkha' bzhin //
NG0423:3488: skal ldan rnal 'byor sku gsum ngang nas sku gsum klong du skyel //
NG0423:3489: dbang po ya rab gyur pa la //
NG0423:3490: ye nas zang thal chen po bas //
NG0423:3491: bar do med cing skad cig med //
NG0423:3492: da lta nyid du lus ngag sku gsum shar //
NG0423:3493: rang bzhin dag pa'i nam mkha' la //
NG0423:3494: chos nyid dag pa'i ngo bor gnas //
NG0423:3495: de la snang ba zang thal shar //
NG0423:3496: rig pa'i ye shes phyi nang med //
NG0423:3497: ma 'gags gsal sgo zang thal 'od gsal lo //
NG0423:3498: dper na nam mkha' zang thal phyi nang med pa la /
NG0423:3499: khang khyim ra bar byas pas nam mkha' gud du bcad //
NG0423:3500: khang khyim nang gi nam mkha' dang *//
NG0423:3501: rang bzhin khyab pa'i nam mkha' gnyis //
NG0423:3502: mthongs kyi nang na gnyis med sgrib med zang thal ltar //
NG0423:3503: bag chags sha khrag sbubs kyi rig pa dang *//
NG0423:3505: chos nyid ye shes dbyings kyi rig pa gnyis //
NG0423:3506: ye shes sgron ma'i sgo yis mtshams sbyar nas //
NG0423:3507: ye shes zang thal chen po rtogs pa yis //
NG0423:3508: bar do skye dang 'gag med par //
NG0423:3509: thabs ma 'gags pa'i ye shes dang *//
NG0423:3510: shes rab 'gyur ba med pa'i chos //
NG0423:3511: rtogs pa'i don chen de ldan na //
NG0423:3512: seng ge mchongs ltar sa bcad pa //
NG0423:3513: rin chen sbubs su ma btsal chod //
NG0423:3515: gdangs kyi snang ba 'od snang shar //
NG0423:3519: chos nyid snang ba chos sku bdal khyab mthong *//
NG0423:3520: rtsol bas rtogs par rdzogs par mngon sangs tshe 'dir rgyas //
NG0423:3521: snang ba rgyas 'debs pa dgongs pa des mthar skyol //
NG0423:3522: zhes seng ge sgra yi dgongs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0423:3523: sku gsum rtsal gyi snang ba dbyings ye shes la
NG0423:3524: sdud par bstan pa'i le'u ste don bdun pa'o //
NG0423:3525: // kye / bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / dngos grub thob pa ji ltar grol //
NG0423:3526: le lo can gyi gang zag la //
NG0423:3527: bar do grol ba ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3529: mkha' spyod dngos grub thob pa ni //
NG0423:3530: ye shes sgyu ma'i snang ba la //
NG0423:3531: gnyis med spyod pas mkha' spyod grol //
NG0423:3532: bar do grol ba'i grol lugs la //
NG0423:3533: 'khrul pa'i snang ba ji ltar 'gag / rang la
NG0423:3534: shes pa ji ltar 'jug / 'chi rtags rim pa
NG0423:3535: ji ltar 'byung *// ye shes snang ba ji ltar 'char //
NG0423:3536: dbang 'bring grol lugs ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3539: dang po rang la shar bas na //
NG0423:3540: tha ma rang gi ngang du grol //
NG0423:3542: mtshan ma rang sar grol gyur pa //
NG0423:3544: yul lnga sgo lnga'i gnas su sdud //
NG0423:3545: sgo lnga 'byung ba lnga la sdud //
NG0423:3546: 'byung lnga yum lnga bum pa'i dbyings su sdud //
NG0423:3547: gzung 'dzin sems rtog ye shes lnga la sdud //
NG0423:3548: ye shes gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ngo bo chos kyi sku /
NG0423:3549: kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba rang gdangs 'od du 'dus //
NG0423:3550: mkha' la 'ja' tshon gsal ba lta bu de //
NG0423:3551: ye shes gsal ba mtha' dbus med par khyab //
NG0423:3552: de tshe rin chen nyi zla kha sbyor klong na bzhugs //
NG0423:3553: 'byed med shes rab ye shes klong dril nas //
NG0423:3554: skad cig dang po bag chags sbubs na gnas dus so //
NG0423:3555: rig pa 'od la 'jug pa bstan pa ni //
NG0423:3556: dwangs ma 'byung ba rnam pa lnga //
NG0423:3557: chos nyid snying po'i 'od la shar //
NG0423:3558: phyi yi snang ba'i 'byung ba lnga //
NG0423:3559: mi snang rang rang ngang du thim //
NG0423:3560: rin chen rtsa nas rig pa ni //
NG0423:3561: 'od la sgron mar zhugs nas kyang *//
NG0423:3562: bag chags sbubs ni zla ba lta bu nas //
NG0423:3563: chos nyid nam mkha'i dbyings la ni //
NG0423:3564: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor nyi ma lta bur 'pho //
NG0423:3565: ye shes rang sa rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis //
NG0423:3566: kun tu 'od la sku gsum mthar bskyal gces //
NG0423:3567: nyi zla kha sbyor gdams pa rtogs par bya //
NG0423:3569: snang ba 'gags pa dang rig pa sgron mar 'jug pa'i le'u ste don brgyad pa'o ///
NG0423:3571: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / bag chags sha khrag sbubs nas ni //
NG0423:3572: ye shes sbubs su 'pho ba la //
NG0423:3573: rtags kyi rim pa ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3576: sa nyid sa thim 'degs pa'i rtsal nyams te //
NG0423:3577: lus lci shes pa thim pa yin //
NG0423:3578: de nas chu la chu thim ste //
NG0423:3579: sdud pa'i nus nyams kha sna skam la med //
NG0423:3580: me la me thim drod nyams @#//
NG0423:3582: lus kyi drod 'pho rkang pa grang *//
NG0423:3583: rlung la rlung thim g.yo ba'i nus pa nyams //
NG0423:3584: lus kyi shes pa rdib cing skyod pa'i nus pa nyams //
NG0423:3585: rnam shes nam mkhar thim nas tshor ba bde sdug rtog bral lo //
NG0423:3586: 'byung ba thim pas 'khrul pa 'gag pa ni //
NG0423:3587: 'degs pa sa yi rlung ni tshogs pa la gnas te //
NG0423:3588: de nyid nyams pas 'degs pa'i nus pa med //
NG0423:3589: chu yi rlung ni lus kun bkrag dang gzi mdangs gnas //
NG0423:3590: de nyams bkrag dang gzi nyams mdangs med lus phra 'dar //
NG0423:3591: me dang mnyam rlung pho bar gnas te drod 'chor zas mi 'ju //
NG0423:3592: rlung gi rlung ni steng sgo 'og sgor gnas bcas nas //
NG0423:3593: dwangs snyigs 'byed de thig le dri chu mchil snabs 'dor //
NG0423:3594: de nyams shas lji shes pa bying la myos //
NG0423:3595: snying rje med pa las kyi rlung zhes pa //
NG0423:3596: 'khor rlung srog rtsa glo nas rgyu ba ste //
NG0423:3597: srog 'dzin yin pas ji srid gnas par srog 'dzin no //
NG0423:3598: rnam shes rig pa ye shes rlung *//
NG0423:3599: skyod pa tsit+ta sgron mar skyod byed do //
NG0423:3600: 'od lam dar skud rtsa nas skyod //
NG0423:3601: rtags kyi gsang sgor phyin pa dang *//
NG0423:3602: dper na shar rir nyi shar bas //
NG0423:3604: phyi yul zer 'od snang ba ni //
NG0423:3605: rig pa ye shes sgron ma nas //
NG0423:3606: chos nyid nam mkha' yul gsal 'od //
NG0423:3607: ye shes 'od zer zang thal ba //
NG0423:3610: rang gi gdangs la zer 'phro ba //
NG0423:3611: skar ma lta bu'i snang ba'am //
NG0423:3612: srin bu me khyer du ba'am //
NG0423:3613: 'ja' 'am smig sgyu lta bur zer phran 'char //
NG0423:3615: 'byung ba rtags kyi le'u ste don dgu pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3616: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / 'byung ba'i 'chi rtags shar nas ni //
NG0423:3617: dbang po so so snang ba yin //
NG0423:3619: 'khrul pa yul snang ji ltar 'gag / ye shes zhi la 'bros pa'i rtags //
NG0423:3620: rlung rnams rim gyis zhi gyur nas //
NG0423:3621: las kyi rlung gis ye shes mkha' la skyod //
NG0423:3622: 'chi bdag rlung gi grong khyer nas //
NG0423:3623: bdud kyi so pa chas sam brtag / lus kyi dbang po sa yi rlung 'gags pas //
NG0423:3625: spyod lam rnams 'gag ngo tsha bral bar byed //
NG0423:3626: lce yi dbang po rlung nyams pas //
NG0423:3627: zas kyi ro yi tshor ba 'gag / sna yi dbang po me yi rlung nyams pas //
NG0423:3628: dri yang tshor bar mi 'gyur la //
NG0423:3630: dbugs kyang rab tu thung zhing brtsegs //
NG0423:3631: rna ba'i dbang po rlung nyams pas //
NG0423:3632: sgra yang mi thos log sgrar thos //
NG0423:3633: rnam shes nam mkha'i rlung nyams pas //
NG0423:3634: gzugs 'gag mi ngo shes par mi 'gyur ro //
NG0423:3635: 'byung ba lnga yang dwangs ma lnga la 'dus //
NG0423:3636: dwangs ma lnga nyid longs sku 'od la 'du //
NG0423:3637: sa yi dwangs ma nya mig tsam //
NG0423:3638: rdo rje sems dpa' 'od zer dkar por thim //
NG0423:3639: chu yi dwangs ma bye'u lan pa'i mgo tsam la //
NG0423:3640: rin chen 'byung ldan 'od zer ser por thim //
NG0423:3641: drod kyi dwangs ma me long nyid 'od tsam //
NG0423:3644: rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og ngad pa tsam //
NG0423:3645: don yod grub pa 'od zer ljang khur thim //
NG0423:3646: 'byung ba 'od la 'dus te rigs lnga chos skur thim //
NG0423:3647: de nas ye shes sku gsum 'dzin pa'i zer rlung dang *//
NG0423:3648: las rlung 'byung ba srog 'dzin snying rje med pa gnyis //
NG0423:3649: thag pa zer du chad nas dbugs ni sna sgor 'das //
NG0423:3650: rig pa chos sku sgron mar zer zhon nas //
NG0423:3651: sgron ma 'od zhon chos sku chos nyid mkha' la bskyod //
NG0423:3652: gcig skye gcig 'gag ye shes snang ba 'phreng ba brgyud pa'i tshul //
NG0423:3653: de tshe chos nyid ngo bo nyid //
NG0423:3654: rang bzhin dag pa'i nam mkha' dang *//
NG0423:3655: gnyis med gcig med don nyid khyab bdal lo //
NG0423:3656: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:3657: snang ba 'gag pa'i le'u ste brgyad cu pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3658: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / ye shes gdangs kyi rim pa'i snang ba ji ltar 'char //
NG0423:3660: chos sku sgron ma yul nas ye shes lam zhon nas //
NG0423:3661: chos nyid bar dor rang snang rim par rdzogs tshul ni //
NG0423:3662: dang po rang bzhin rim par 'char //
NG0423:3663: zla 'od shar ba lta bu ste //
NG0423:3664: skya yal ba'am dkar yal 'od 'char ro //
NG0423:3665: de phyir rtog pa bzhi bcu 'gag par 'gyur //
NG0423:3666: de nas mched pa'i 'od gsal ni //
NG0423:3667: ye shes snang ba 'ja' ltar kha dog lnga //
NG0423:3668: skad cig dang po mthing kha yul du 'char //
NG0423:3669: rig pa ngos gzung bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NG0423:3670: ye shes rang shar snang ba gsal //
NG0423:3671: de nas skad cig gnyis pa la //
NG0423:3672: dkar po yul du snang ba'i tshe //
NG0423:3673: rig pa 'gag min me long ye shes chod //
NG0423:3674: skad cig gsum la ser po yul du snang *//
NG0423:3675: rig stong dbyer med mnyam nyid ye shes chod //
NG0423:3676: skad cig bzhi la 'od gdangs dmar po yul du snang ba'i tshe //
NG0423:3677: so sor rtog pa ye shes gdangs su chod //
NG0423:3678: skad cig lnga la ljang khu yul du snang ba'i tshe //
NG0423:3679: rang snang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes gdangs su chod //
NG0423:3680: ye shes mched pa'i snang ba rim gyi skye ba nam langs 'dra //
NG0423:3681: chos pa rtogs pa re re thad kar chod //
NG0423:3682: gzung 'dzin rtog pa med pas shes bya gud gcod med //
NG0423:3683: de nang rtog pa sum cu rtsa gsum 'gag pa'o //
NG0423:3684: ye shes lnga yi snang ba rdzogs nas thob pa'i 'od gsal ni //
NG0423:3685: shes rab kyi ngo bo mthar phyin pa //
NG0423:3686: skad cig chos nyid 'od gsal dkyil 'khor na //
NG0423:3687: thob pa'i ye shes 'od gsal sku gsum lhun mnyam pa //
NG0423:3688: phyag rgya ma 'gags gzhi rdzogs chos kyi sku //
NG0423:3689: ye shes sgo lnga ma 'gags nyi ma shar ba lta bur thob //
NG0423:3690: thob pas gsang rtog bu bdun 'gags so //
NG0423:3691: de nas chos nyid bar do thob pa'i 'od gsal zhes su bya //
NG0423:3692: seng ge sgra sgrogs theg dman zil gyis gnon pa nyi zla kha sbyor rgyud las /
NG0423:3693: ye shes snang ba 'char ba'i le'u ste gya gcig pa'o ///
NG0423:3695: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / chos nyid bar do de
NG0423:3698: rtogs pa'i shes rab skal ldan rang shar bas //
NG0423:3699: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rdzogs sangs ji ltar rgya //
NG0423:3701: chos sku kha dog sna tshogs 'od 'bar bas //
NG0423:3702: ngo bo nyid kyi sku las ni //
NG0423:3703: ngo bo nyid kyi skur shar ba //
NG0423:3704: 'od bum lnga la rig pa'i ye shes bzhugs //
NG0423:3705: mthong ba'i gzugs yod rig min longs sku lnga //
NG0423:3706: tshom bu sems dpar bcas pa rim 'jug skad cig 'char //
NG0423:3707: ngo bo nyid rang dang 'dra ba rdo rje sems dpar shar //
NG0423:3708: ye shes snang ba me long lta bur rtogs //
NG0423:3710: des skye med chos sku'i srog kyang bzung *//
NG0423:3711: rin 'byung snang la so sor rtogs pa shar //
NG0423:3712: ye shes so sor gsal bas dpe byad brgyad cu dang *//
NG0423:3713: mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis stobs ni bco brgyad ldan //
NG0423:3714: stobs lnga ni byang chub yan lag rdzogs //
NG0423:3715: mtha' yas rang las shar bas mnyam nyid ye shes gsal //
NG0423:3716: der sangs rgyas gzigs pa bsam gyis mi khyab gsal //
NG0423:3717: rnam dag thugs shar zhing khams sku gsum bcas pa mthong *//
NG0423:3718: 'gro drug snang ba rdul dang rdul phran gzigs //
NG0423:3719: rgya mtsho thigs par bgrang dang skye gnas sdug bsngal mthong *//
NG0423:3720: 'gro drug rnams kyi las dang bsam pa kun kyang mthong *//
NG0423:3721: ngo bo nyid las don yod grub pa shar bas ni //
NG0423:3722: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes rang la shar //
NG0423:3724: ngo bo nyid las rnam par snang mdzad shar //
NG0423:3725: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes rang la rdzogs //
NG0423:3726: des sku lnga ye shes lnga rdzogs rang la rang nyid snang *//
NG0423:3727: des sems dpa' sems ma sgo ba rang shar gnas //
NG0423:3728: man shel lta bur sku gsum phyi nang med //
NG0423:3729: rang la snang bar mdzad pas rnam snang chen pos bya'o //
NG0423:3730: rig pa'i lha mo'i sgo la 'jug pa'i tshe //
NG0423:3731: ye shes rig pa ma pang bu rgyug 'dra //
NG0423:3732: ye shes rang snang 'dam gyi pad+ma 'dra //
NG0423:3733: rang sa zin pa nyi ma'i snying po 'dra //
NG0423:3734: der mkhyen pa thob pa'i drug pa rdo rje 'chang *//
NG0423:3735: thugs rje 'byung ba yi ge drug gi 'gro don mdzad //
NG0423:3736: thub drug 'gro don zad nas sems dpa' las zad nas //
NG0423:3737: thugs rje mtha' zad ye shes klong du grol //
NG0423:3738: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa las /
NG0423:3739: rnal 'byor mngon sangs rgyas par bstan pa'i le'u ste gya gnyis pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3740: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / bar do ngo bo nges tshig dang *//
NG0423:3741: dbye ba bye brag ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3743: bar do ngo bo ma 'dres sku gsum la //
NG0423:3744: nges tshig sems can lnga lus bor //
NG0423:3745: phyi ma sems de ma blangs pas //
NG0423:3746: bar na sku gsum rang shar na //
NG0423:3747: rgyu rkyen med pa snga phyir bar na sangs rgyas de bos bya //
NG0423:3748: dbye ba mang yang chos nyid bar do srid pa bar do'o //
NG0423:3749: mtshan nyid 'byung lnga mal zha rnam shes dbyings su thim //
NG0423:3754: de dus chos nyid bar do rang bzhin ni //
NG0423:3755: rang byung dkyil 'khor nam mkha' shar zhes bya //
NG0423:3756: rnal 'byor rang ngo shes pa grol ba'i sa //
NG0423:3757: yun dus ji tsam gnas ngan ni //
NG0423:3758: sems can tshe bral dus su yang *//
NG0423:3759: zhag lnga bar du bde dang ldan //
NG0423:3760: de yi dus na tshor ba bde sdug bral //
NG0423:3761: khyung phrug dang ni seng phrug ltar //
NG0423:3762: rnal 'byor lus rgya grol zhes bya //
NG0423:3763: tshe bral skye gnas mod mi len //
NG0423:3764: len na sems can nyid rgyud pas //
NG0423:3765: bka' lung 'gro la phan mi thogs par 'gyur //
NG0423:3766: rnam shes gzhir thim snga phyi lus ma blangs //
NG0423:3767: lus med phyir na sems skye srog rtsa med //
NG0423:3768: lus med phyir na sems rten tsit+ta med //
NG0423:3769: de yi phyir na sems sam sgo gsum med //
NG0423:3770: de phyir sems rda dbugs kyang med //
NG0423:3771: de phyir sems kyis 'gro drug gnas mi len zhes bya //
NG0423:3772: des na chos nyid bar do ye shes dbyings kyi gzhi //
NG0423:3773: skyon gyis ma gos spyi yi yon tan ni //
NG0423:3774: sku gsum rtogs pa ma shar mkhyen pa'i sar mi gnas //
NG0423:3775: bag chags mtshams ma sbyar bas bar dol mi gnas //
NG0423:3776: sa lam rang sa snga bas sa dang lam mi gnas //
NG0423:3777: skye ba ma blangs 'gro drug la mi gnas //
NG0423:3778: mi gnas gzhi yis sku gsum rang ngor gsal //
NG0423:3779: snga phyi lus med sgrib pa ma sbyangs dag /
NG0423:3780: rnam shes gzhir thim nyon mongs ma spangs dag /
NG0423:3781: skye gnas ma blangs 'khor ba ma spangs dag /
NG0423:3782: rang byung dkyil 'khor rang shar snang srid dag /
NG0423:3783: dag pa gzhi yis sku gsum dri med bstan //
NG0423:3784: snga phyi lus kyi sgrib shing med //
NG0423:3785: sku gsum chos nyid sgrib pa'i dbang ma song *//
NG0423:3786: rigs drug lus sems med pas nyon mongs dbang ma song *//
NG0423:3787: dge sdig sems ma bskyed pas bag chags dbang ma song *//
NG0423:3788: 'gro drug lus ma blangs pa las kyi dbang ma song *//
NG0423:3789: dbang du ma song gzhi yis sku gsum spyi sa bstan //
NG0423:3790: 'gro drug ma blangs skye gnas bar ma gcad //
NG0423:3791: bag chags mtshams ma sbyar bas bar dor bas ma gcad //
NG0423:3792: sa lam ma bgrod sa lam bar mi gcad //
NG0423:3793: bar ma gcad pas sku gsum dkyil 'khor rang sar bstan //
NG0423:3794: de ltar bar do spyi yi yon tan ni //
NG0423:3795: bco lnga yongs la khyab par bstan pa'o //
NG0423:3796: zhes seng ge sgra nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:3797: bar do spyi yi bye brag rnam par bshad pa'i le'u ste gya gsum pa'o //  // kye /
NG0423:3798: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / spyi sa bar do ye grol gnas //
NG0423:3800: gdams pa bar dor rang grol bstan //
NG0423:3801: de yi gdams ngag ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3802: rang bzhin gnas kyi bar do la //
NG0423:3803: rgyud lung kun gyi don bkrol la //
NG0423:3804: ngo sprod gsum gyis gtan la dbab //
NG0423:3805: rang rig rtogs pas thag bcad nas //
NG0423:3806: dgongs pa rang shar gsal ba dang *//
NG0423:3808: chos nyid bar dor ye shes ngos gzung la //
NG0423:3809: longs sku rdo rje 'dzin par mngon sangs rgyas par bya //
NG0423:3810: srid pa bar dor las kyi 'phro @#//
NG0423:3812: rdo rje sems dpar sems kyang gdab //
NG0423:3813: blo dman skye ba phyi mar bag chags rjes grol bya //
NG0423:3814: tshe bral mod du skye ba mi len pa //
NG0423:3815: chos nyid bar do 'gro kun 'char nges der //
NG0423:3816: skal ldan grol ba'i gdams pa bka' stsal pa //
NG0423:3817: ye shes rang snang skyon med 'dam gyi pad+ma la //
NG0423:3818: rig pa rang sa nyi ma'i snying po lta bur gzung *//
NG0423:3819: chos nyid gnas lugs snga phyi lus kyi sgrib pa med //
NG0423:3820: sku gsum 'od gsal 'ja' tshon lta bu gcer bur gnas //
NG0423:3821: yin lugs gzung 'dzin gzhir thim rig par gcer bu'i thugs //
NG0423:3822: 'char lugs las rlung lus sems 'brel med 'od zer gcer bur gnas //
NG0423:3823: gcer bu rnam gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3824: bag chags sbubs ni nyi zla gzas zin 'dra //
NG0423:3825: 'khor du 'khor sa med pa gzhan snang dag pa'i rang snang shar //
NG0423:3826: gol du gol sa med pa rang nyid dkyil 'khor shar //
NG0423:3827: 'khrul du 'khrul sa med pa gdams ngag rtogs pa'i shes rab shar //
NG0423:3828: gegs sel rnam gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3829: lam 'bras sa lam tshol byed pa //
NG0423:3830: byang thang lus pa'i mgron bu 'dra //
NG0423:3831: sku gsum 'od gsal ye shar bas //
NG0423:3832: kun tu 'od la gnas pa'i sa //
NG0423:3833: mi thob rang dbang med pa'i gnad //
NG0423:3834: ngo bo sku gsum ye sangs rgyas //
NG0423:3835: skye shi rgyun chod nges pa'i gnad //
NG0423:3836: ye shes sgo lnga zang thal bas //
NG0423:3837: mthong ba'i yul la gdams ngag rang ngo mi rtog dbang med gnad //
NG0423:3838: gdams ngag gnad gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3839: gying ling sgrog tu bcug pa 'dra //
NG0423:3840: 'bras bu rang sar ga la phyin //
NG0423:3841: rang snang pho brang zer 'od gsal yang btab //
NG0423:3842: sku gsum ngo bo'i snang bas gsal yang btab //
NG0423:3843: rig pa gdams ngag rkyen du shar bas gsal yang btab //
NG0423:3844: gsal 'debs rnam gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3845: me long g.ya' yis bsgribs pa 'dra //
NG0423:3846: 'od zer lam ston yid ches rdeb pa'i gzer //
NG0423:3847: sku gsum don chod 'khor ba ru log gzer //
NG0423:3848: rang shar dgongs pa 'gyur med rgyun du bcas //
NG0423:3849: ye shes sgo lnga rang ngo rang la mi gsal thabs med gzer //
NG0423:3850: gzer bu rnam gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3851: ko skya med pa'i gru ba 'dra //
NG0423:3852: rang snang chos dbyings pho brang ni //
NG0423:3853: kun gzhi me long zang thal bas //
NG0423:3854: phyi yi snang ba gzung yul med par mngon sangs rgyas //
NG0423:3855: rang byung sku gsum dkyil 'khor ni //
NG0423:3856: 'od gsal chos dbyings me long ste //
NG0423:3857: zang thal shar bas lus kyi sgrib shing med //
NG0423:3858: 'khor ba'i rtod phur med par mngon sangs rgyas //
NG0423:3859: thugs kyi rig pa chos nyid rang shar bas //
NG0423:3860: thugs rig pa'i me long gzung 'dzin bag chags dag
NG0423:3861: / 'gyur byed zang thal rig par mngon sangs rgyas
NG0423:3862: // me long rnam gsum ma shes na //
NG0423:3863: mun pa srod pa'i skar ma dang 'dra //
NG0423:3864: de ltar don nyid bco brgyad kyis //
NG0423:3865: rtogs pa'i shes rab thams cad mkhyen par 'char //
NG0423:3867: gsal dkyil 'khor de la rgyu rkyen med //
NG0423:3868: rang grol rig pa de la bcos ma bslad //
NG0423:3869: rang shar dgongs pa sems kyis ma gzung ste //
NG0423:3870: sku gsum rang sa dngos las 'bras bu'i spogs mi tshol //
NG0423:3871: lhun grub ye shes de las 'pho 'gyur gnas mi sod //
NG0423:3872: de yi gnad dang gzer gsum bstan pa ni //
NG0423:3873: phyi yi snang ba chos nyid rang gdangs shar //
NG0423:3874: 'khor bar lus sems 'tshogs sa med pa'i gzer //
NG0423:3875: thugs kyi mkhyen pa ye shes gdangs su shar //
NG0423:3876: gzung 'dzin sems su 'gyur mi srid pa'i gzer //
NG0423:3877: gsung gi zer gdangs 'od zer zang thal bas //
NG0423:3878: lus sems las kyi rlung gis sgra mi srid pa'i gzer //
NG0423:3879: rang snang zang thal rtog sgrib med //
NG0423:3880: rang rig rang gsal mkhyen par shar //
NG0423:3881: sgo lnga 'od gsal sgrib med rang sar grol //
NG0423:3882: bgrod du med pa'i grol ba'i gzer zhes bya'o //
NG0423:3883: mkhyen pa longs sku ye shes rdzogs par 'char ba'i gzer bstan pa //
NG0423:3884: rang gsal sku yi khyab bdal sku nyid mkhyen par shar //
NG0423:3885: ngo bo nyid chos kyi sku las ni //
NG0423:3886: ngo bo nyid kyi sku shar ba //
NG0423:3887: rang dang mnyam bzhi lha bzhi bcur shar //
NG0423:3888: rang shar thugs kyi khyab bdal rig pa'i rang gdangs mkhyen par shar //
NG0423:3889: thugs dang mnyam pa'i rig pa ye shes longs sku khyab par zhugs //
NG0423:3891: rang grol gsung gi khyab bdal zer gdangs chos kyi sgo mor shar //
NG0423:3892: brjod med don dang mnyam pa'i sgra dang tshig / zer 'od sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong 'char //
NG0423:3893: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam dag mkhyen pa rnam dag phyogs med do //
NG0423:3894: de ltar rnal 'byor grol ba'i sa tshad ni //
NG0423:3896: chos nyid bar do srid pa'i la tshig yin //
NG0423:3897: rnal 'byor rtog pa klong gyur dus mnyam bdun gyis grol //
NG0423:3898: 'jug dang snang dang shes pa dang *//
NG0423:3899: thob grol mkhyen pa thugs rje mnyam //
NG0423:3901: zhes seng ge sgra sgrogs theg dman zil gyis gnon pa'i rgyud las /
NG0423:3902: bar dor mngon sangs rgyas pa'i gdams ngag gdab ba'i le'u ste gya bzhi pa'o ///
NG0423:3904: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / grol ba'i sku gsum mkhyen pa de //
NG0423:3905: skyon bral dag pa ji ltar lags //
NG0423:3907: ye shes sgrib med ma rig rang grol ba //
NG0423:3908: 'od gsal zang thal shar bas rtsal gyi sgrib pa med //
NG0423:3909: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa las grol //
NG0423:3910: mthong ba'i yul la rtogs pa'i shes rab shar //
NG0423:3911: des bag chags bsgribs pa med //
NG0423:3912: bag chags rgyun med rmongs pa'i ma rig pa las grol //
NG0423:3913: sku gsum dkyil 'khor rang shar bas //
NG0423:3914: kun tu brtag pa ma rig pa las grol //
NG0423:3915: ye shes sgo lnga zang thal shar ba yis //
NG0423:3916: nyon mongs sgrib med ma rig pa las grol //
NG0423:3917: sku gsum rang ngo shes pas 'khor ba yi //
NG0423:3918: gting thag las dang las kyi sgrib med ces bya //
NG0423:3919: sgrib pa med pa mkhyen pa rang sar bstan //
NG0423:3920: de ni 'khor ba'i 'khrul pa zhig pa yin //
NG0423:3922: gsum ye shes rtogs pas gzhan snang 'khrul ba zhig
NG0423:3923: / sku gsum skye 'jig med pas lus kyi 'khrul
NG0423:3924: pa zhig / gsung gi nyi 'od zer 'phro bas
NG0423:3925: ngag gi 'khrul pa zhig / thugs la mkhyen pa
NG0423:3926: rig pas gzung 'dzin yid sems 'khrul ba zhig /
NG0423:3927: rlung gis sems sgral ba med pas 'byung ba'i 'khrul
NG0423:3928: pa zhig / srid par sbyor ba med pas skye
NG0423:3929: gnas 'khrul pa zhig / ye shes nyi ma shar
NG0423:3930: bas gsal 'grib nyi nub 'khrul pa zhig / zhag
NG0423:3931: dang lo zla 'das pas dus kyi 'khrul pa zhig
NG0423:3932: / chos nyid pho brang thig ler 'khyil bas phyogs
NG0423:3933: kyi 'khrul pa zhig / ces seng ge sgra'i rgyud
NG0423:3934: las / grol ba mngon gyur sangs rgyas sgrib pa
NG0423:3935: dag ste ma rig pa grol nas 'khrul pa zhig
NG0423:3936: mkhyen pa thob pa'i le'u ste gya lnga pa'o //
NG0423:3937: las / // kye / bcom ldan thugs rje thabs
NG0423:3938: kyi bdag / gang zag skal ba zhan dang blo
NG0423:3939: dman dang */ / theg dman blo yi bcos dang
NG0423:3940: las / // kye / rtsol ba zhan // chos nyid bar dor rtogs par ma gyur na //
NG0423:3941: thabs kyi lam gyis ji ltar grol bar bgyi //
NG0423:3943: kye rdo rje 'dzin pas nges par zungs shig / shes rab rtogs pa'i blo can gyis //
NG0423:3944: mchog gi 'od gsal chen po la //
NG0423:3945: rig pa zang thal shar ba gces //
NG0423:3946: de yis tshe 'dir bar do med par grol //
NG0423:3947: skyes bu las dang skal ldan ni //
NG0423:3948: mchog gi 'od gsal chung ngu de //
NG0423:3949: chos nyid ma yi bar do la //
NG0423:3951: mkhyen pa'i shes rab shar ba gces //
NG0423:3952: srid pa'i bar do med par grol //
NG0423:3953: blo dman bar dor rim 'jug la //
NG0423:3954: rig pa'i rang sa zin pa gces //
NG0423:3955: des kyang sa lam med par grol //
NG0423:3958: rig pa 'gro ldog shes pa gces //
NG0423:3959: de yis srid pa bar do ye shes sogs kyang thebs //
NG0423:3960: de yis gdams ngag gsal 'debs dus //
NG0423:3961: rig pa mngon du shar ba gces //
NG0423:3962: de yis yi dam rdo rje sems dpa'i srog kyang zin //
NG0423:3963: chos nyid bar do 'da' ba ni //
NG0423:3964: ngo bo chos sku thugs kyi zer //
NG0423:3965: yum gyi rang bzhin bum pa lnga la yid kyi 'gyu ba zhugs //
NG0423:3966: dang po som nyi mtshams sbyor te //
NG0423:3967: ci yin mnyam pa'i yid tsam 'gyus //
NG0423:3968: de nas bag chags rtog sgrib spogs 'debs te //
NG0423:3969: dus kyi snyigs ma kha drag lam dang 'dra //
NG0423:3970: srid pa'i skye gnas dug gi me tog 'dra //
NG0423:3971: 'khor bar 'jug pa zo'i chu khyud mo 'dra //
NG0423:3972: som nyi rang 'od zer las bar do 'od lus blangs //
NG0423:3973: ci yin snyam pas yin min shes pa zhugs //
NG0423:3974: chos nyid bar do nyi ma shar ba lta bu la //
NG0423:3975: rtog pa phra ba gsang rtog bdun skyes pas //
NG0423:3976: chos nyid ye shes snang ba dag pa la //
NG0423:3977: nam mkha'i sprin lta bu yi srubs la byung *//
NG0423:3978: de las ngan rtog sum cu rtsa gsum ji rags snang *//
NG0423:3979: de nyid chos nyid bar do nyi ma rtog pas nam srod lta bur nub //
NG0423:3980: de nas phyi rtog bzhi bcu spogs //
NG0423:3981: mun pa srod pas skar ma shar ba ltar //
NG0423:3985: de la 'od gsal chung ngu gdams pa ye shes sogs gdab pa //
NG0423:3986: 'di ni skal ba zhan dang blo dman le lo can //
NG0423:3987: chos nyid bar dor rang grol ma thob na //
NG0423:3988: gsang lam bsegs lam thabs kyis grol ba'i lam zhes bya //
NG0423:3989: 'di la skyel bsu yin par shes pa gnad yin te //
NG0423:3990: bla ma lung ldan gdams ngag skyel ma dang *//
NG0423:3992: rang gis nyams su longs te rtogs pa'i skyel ma dang *//
NG0423:3993: 'chi khar gsal 'debs grogs kyi skyel ma gces //
NG0423:3994: zer gyi bsun mas 'od zer lam bstan nas //
NG0423:3995: 'od lnga bsun mas zhing khams dag par skyel //
NG0423:3996: sgra yi bsun ma sku gsum dkyil 'khor thob //
NG0423:3997: chos nyid 'das pa yin par shes nas ni //
NG0423:3998: srid pa bar do sngon gzugs srid pa'i sha gzugs can //
NG0423:3999: dbang po kun tshang 'od kyi lus de la //
NG0423:4000: yi chad drug 'byung shi ba dran nas skye gnas tshol //
NG0423:4001: las kyi dge sdig gshin rje'i snang ba ston //
NG0423:4002: de dus gdams pa yin par shes par bya //
NG0423:4003: srid pa'i bar do de ni rang bzhin las //
NG0423:4004: chos nyid bar dor rtogs pas ma grol na //
NG0423:4006: nges par bar do 'od lus len dang gcig / sngar gyi bag chags rtog pa dran dang gnyis //
NG0423:4008: sngar dran phyis skye de rang shes pa'i shes rab gsum //
NG0423:4009: yid lus 'od kyi sgo lngas 'gro drug mthong nges bzhi //
NG0423:4010: sgyu ma ye shes lus yin dran gsal blo rno lnga'o //
NG0423:4011: de yang sems de sku gsum brgyud nas brgyud mar gnas pa na //
NG0423:4012: ci ste da ltar bag chags sbubs nas sprul sku ste //
NG0423:4013: skad cig mi grol ye shes lam la sbyangs //
NG0423:4014: rin chen zang thal sbubs na chos skur gnas //
NG0423:4015: skad cig dang po ngang la dus mnyam rtog pas grol //
NG0423:4016: longs sku sgyu ma 'od kyi sbubs la skad cig gsum gyis grol //
NG0423:4017: sgyu ma 'od lus srid pa'i sha gzugs la //
NG0423:4018: rtog pa rkun bu bag la nyal ba de //
NG0423:4019: dran pa'i som nyi kun nas ldang ba'o //
NG0423:4020: kun nas ldang ba'i yid sems de //
NG0423:4021: snga phyi da lta'i rtog pa shes rab skyes pa'i dus //
NG0423:4022: shin tu blo rno dran pa gsal bas na //
NG0423:4023: de la grol ba'i gdams pa gsang lam bsegs lam btsal //
NG0423:4024: gdams ngag nyams su blangs pa sngar shugs kyis //
NG0423:4025: rang dbang dran pa mngon du 'gyur ba yin //
NG0423:4026: de tshe rtogs pa khyad par skye dus yin //
NG0423:4027: sngar gyi nyams len gdams ngag rnams //
NG0423:4028: de tshe mi dran mi srid do //
NG0423:4029: der sngar byas mi dran mi 'byung na //
NG0423:4030: dge sdig las kyi 'bras bu mi 'byung dgos //
NG0423:4031: las mi 'byung bar gyur pas na //
NG0423:4033: des na bka' yi gdams pa dran par nges //
NG0423:4034: khyad par rtogs pa nyams len dang ni rgyal ba'i
NG0423:4035: ngag / dge sdig las ni shin tu gsal ba'i
NG0423:4036: dus // bar do 'od lus yin pas thams cad rang gsal lo //
NG0423:4037: gdams pas ji ltar lam btsal na //
NG0423:4038: 'gro drug grong khyer dran pa dang *//
NG0423:4041: bar do yin pa dran gsal gdab //
NG0423:4042: de rang sgyu lus yin pa dran pa dang *//
NG0423:4043: gnyis med spyod pas sgyu lus bsgyur btub dran //
NG0423:4044: des rdo rje sems dpa' yi dam lhar bsgyur ba dran pa'o //
NG0423:4045: 'od lus sgyu mar shes pas gnyis su med //
NG0423:4046: gar yang bsgyur du btub par shes pa'o //
NG0423:4047: rdo rje sems dpar lus 'phos pas //
NG0423:4048: lam pa'i rdo rje sems dpas bar do rang srog gzung *//
NG0423:4049: skye ba mi len bsam la skye ba 'phos pas khegs //
NG0423:4050: der rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid 'od gsal sku //
NG0423:4051: de rang shar dgongs pa zung zhugs pas //
NG0423:4053: rdo rje rigs 'dzin sa la de nyid bsegs lam thob //
NG0423:4054: sgo lnga ye shes zang thal 'od gsal las //
NG0423:4055: gsang lam zung du bcug pas rdo rje lta bur thob //
NG0423:4056: de la gsang lam dag pa'i gzer gsum ni //
NG0423:4057: ye shes sgyu lus rdo rje sems dpa' de //
NG0423:4058: rang rig gzhan rig rig pa'i thugs gsal bas //
NG0423:4059: 'od gsal sgrib med ye shes spogs kyang thebs //
NG0423:4060: sku gsum 'od gsal rang snang dkyil 'khor spogs kyang thebs //
NG0423:4061: bla ma'i gdams pa rang shar dgongs pa spogs kyang thebs //
NG0423:4062: de gang zhig rtogs se zhes pa na //
NG0423:4063: byang chub sems lam rigs 'dzin sa yin pas //
NG0423:4064: chos nyid can ni cha gang tshad du shar //
NG0423:4065: mngon par shes dang mi rtog ting 'dzin yod //
NG0423:4066: mngon par shes pas gdams ngag snga phyir shes //
NG0423:4067: ting 'dzin rdo rje sems dpa' lam gyi srog kyang 'dzin //
NG0423:4068: dgongs pas srog ni ji ltar 'dzin zhe na //
NG0423:4070: mtshan bcas 'od lus lhar bsgyur nas //
NG0423:4071: mtshan med rig pa'i 'od gsal rang grol chos //
NG0423:4072: stong gsal rang shar 'gyur med ngang la srog kyang gzung *//
NG0423:4073: 'gro drug grong khyer 'khor ba zang thal shes //
NG0423:4074: des ye shes lus la skye ba gzhan mi len //
NG0423:4075: bar do rten 'brel sgyu lus 'od gsal bas //
NG0423:4076: 'dod pas len pa'i skye gnas gzhan mi tshol //
NG0423:4077: sku gsum lhun grub rang la rtogs pa pas sa lam rang grol chod //
NG0423:4078: des mchog gis 'od gsal spogs thebs mngon sangs rgyas //
NG0423:4079: zhes seng ge sgra nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:4080: 'od gsal chung ngu+u ye shes sman du byung ba'i le'u ste gya drug pa'o ///
NG0423:4082: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / chos nyid bar do ye shes lam la ma grol na //
NG0423:4083: blo dman bag chags sad de skye ba brgyud nas grol lugs ji ltar lags //
NG0423:4085: 'gro ba de yi skye gnas len lugs ni //
NG0423:4087: zhag lnga skad cig lnga la chos nyid bar do la 'das na //
NG0423:4088: skad cig drug la som nyi za bar byed //
NG0423:4089: skad cig bdun na bar do 'od lus len //
NG0423:4090: de nas yi chad shi ba rjes su dran //
NG0423:4091: chos nyid bar do ye shes nyi ma'i dmar thag chad //
NG0423:4092: bdun nam bcu bzhi nyi shu rtsa gcig bar //
NG0423:4094: kun tu tshol ba'i yid kyis dran nas thogs med skye gnas tshol //
NG0423:4095: 'gyu byed nya mig tsam gyis 'khrul snang @#//
NG0423:4097: ye shes mun srod 'gro drug 'od kyi lam //
NG0423:4098: tshom bu dar 'phyang tsam lnga shar gyis 'byung *//
NG0423:4099: me 'od lam dmar po cog tu zhugs pa snang *//
NG0423:4101: mngal gyi grong khyer dug gi me tog 'dra //
NG0423:4102: der tshud dga' dang bde ba las //
NG0423:4103: 'dod pa'i bag la nyal nas 'dug tsa na //
NG0423:4104: pha yi sa bon klad pa'i rtsa las babs //
NG0423:4105: ma yi sa bon snying gi rtsa las dmar la dwangs //
NG0423:4106: dmar dwangs dkar 'dril srid pa'i lus la g.yogs //
NG0423:4108: sngon 'byung srid pa'i lus de las kyi shugs kyis gon //
NG0423:4109: pha la zhe sdang ma la chags gyur te //
NG0423:4110: rang gi lus kyi chags lugs dang *//
NG0423:4111: dbang po don snying chags lugs shes //
NG0423:4112: de ltar bar do lus zhig nas //
NG0423:4113: nor bu rin chen rgya mtsho gting tu krog gis ltung *//
NG0423:4114: snying po'i don nyid sna tshogs 'bad pa'i sku //
NG0423:4116: rig pa nyid las 'od lnga bum pa 'phro //
NG0423:4117: ye shes rtsal ma rdzogs pas de la zer phran 'phro //
NG0423:4118: zer nyid dkar po nya mig tsam las sa yi dwangs ma chags //
NG0423:4119: zer nyid ser po chu yi dwangs ma bye'u len pa'i mgo tsam chags //
NG0423:4120: brtan par byed pa sa yin te //
NG0423:4121: sdud par byed pa chu yis byas //
NG0423:4122: krug gis 'dres pa mar ma mer du gnas //
NG0423:4123: zer nyid dmar po drod kyi dwangs ma ni //
NG0423:4124: me long nyi mas tshig pa'i ngang tsam byung *//
NG0423:4125: des lus kyi ngo bo rtsa 'dab brgyad du chags //
NG0423:4126: de nas zer nyid sngon po las //
NG0423:4127: rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og rlangs kyi ngad tsam byung *//
NG0423:4128: ngad de rtsa yi nang du zhugs gyur to //
NG0423:4129: de nas 'og kyi dwangs ma ni //
NG0423:4130: dngul dkar zhun ma thigs pa 'dra ba gcig / snying po'i don la 'ja' tshon lnga yis bskor //
NG0423:4131: rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi dbus nyid du //
NG0423:4133: snying po'i gnas su chags snga ba //
NG0423:4134: sa yi dwangs sems snying chags so //
NG0423:4135: de nas me yis dwangs mas pho mcher chags //
NG0423:4136: de nas chu yi dwangs mas mkhal ma chags //
NG0423:4137: rlung gi dwangs mas glo mchin der chags so //
NG0423:4138: tsit+ta dbus kyi rtsa ni gser gyi ba thag tsam //
NG0423:4139: shel gyi sbu gu dkar 'jam khog stong nang *//
NG0423:4140: rig pa 'od gsal sgron mar rgyu bar byed //
NG0423:4141: gro sog tsam gyi rtsa yis snying dang glo ba sbril //
NG0423:4142: glo ba khog sbugs 'dod pa'i sgo gsum sbrel //
NG0423:4143: kun gzhi sems kyi me long 'od lnga'i pho brang la //
NG0423:4144: gzung 'dzin zer rlung zhon nas glo bar rgyu //
NG0423:4145: don lnga rten bcas lus kyi khog sbubs chags par byas //
NG0423:4146: de nas dbang po chags lugs bstan pa ni //
NG0423:4147: snying po rig pa'i 'od zer ni //
NG0423:4148: rig pa'i 'od lnga bum pa lnga ru shar //
NG0423:4149: de yi zer dkar po yar 'phros pas //
NG0423:4150: shel gyi sbu gus rtsa lam byas //
NG0423:4151: sgal pa'i rten la mig gnyis chags //
NG0423:4152: dran rig zhe sdang rnam gnyis yar la rgyu //
NG0423:4153: zer 'od dmar po mar la rgyus //
NG0423:4154: tshor ba 'gro mdo'i rten la pho mos dbang rten chags //
NG0423:4155: tshor ba'i 'dod chags gnyis ni mar la @#//
NG0423:4157: yar mar rgyu gnyis tshom bu lte ba sbrel //
NG0423:4158: snying po rig pa'i g.yas na yar //
NG0423:4160: rtsa lam kham ser ngan ngan yar //
NG0423:4161: lce yi rten chags nga rgyal rgyu //
NG0423:4162: snying po rig pa'i g.yon na yar //
NG0423:4163: rtsa lam ljang khu nang na yang *//
NG0423:4164: rna ba'i rten chags phra dog rgyu //
NG0423:4165: snying po rig pa'i mdun na yang *//
NG0423:4166: rtsa lam mthing kha nang na yar //
NG0423:4167: sna yi rten chags gti mug rgyu //
NG0423:4168: de nas lus su grub pa ni //
NG0423:4169: snying la gzugs kyi phung po skyed //
NG0423:4170: pho mcher 'du shes phung po skyed //
NG0423:4172: mkhal mas tshor ba'i phung po skyed //
NG0423:4173: glo mchin 'du byed phung po skyed //
NG0423:4174: mchin pas rnam shes phung po skyed //
NG0423:4175: sa yi dwangs mas rus pa chu rgyus skyed //
NG0423:4176: chu yi dwangs mas khrag las sha skyed do //
NG0423:4177: me yis drod dang rlung gis srog rten skyed byed do //
NG0423:4178: nam mkha' go phye 'byung ba'i lus su grub //
NG0423:4179: rig pa'i zer 'gyus rlung gis sems kyi rta byas nas //
NG0423:4180: 'byung ba'i lam rgyu rtsa byung sbubs nas dwangs ma rgyu //
NG0423:4181: snying po rig pa sems kyi sbubs tshud las rlung dbugs phyir rgyu //
NG0423:4182: de ltar chu yi lha mo bum 'dzin ma yis gzugs su bsdus //
NG0423:4183: me yi lha mo 'od gsal ma yis smin //
NG0423:4184: rlung gi lha mo 'degs byed ma yis bteg nas gnas //
NG0423:4185: de nas phyi rol mthong snang ma la skyes //
NG0423:4186: sha khrag sbubs la brten nas dug gsum ngang la spyod //
NG0423:4188: thugs rje lan cig las kyi 'phro sad nas //
NG0423:4189: bcu bzhi lon nas dad pa rjes su dran //
NG0423:4190: bla mas rjes su dran pas rgyal ba'i bka' dang phrad //
NG0423:4191: lus ngag sku gsum dug lnga ye shes lnga ru rtogs //
NG0423:4192: sum cu rtsa bzhi dag la chos sku chos nyid rgyas thebs te //
NG0423:4193: longs sku rtogs pa'i don la rgya yis thebs //
NG0423:4194: sprul sku sgyu ma'i sa la mi rtog ye shes rgya yis thebs //
NG0423:4195: grol ba'i dgongs pa rang la rang shar te //
NG0423:4196: snang ba sgyu mar grol nas smig sgyu tsam du bun tser 'char //
NG0423:4197: nyon mongs rang grol lan tshwa chur zhu bzhin du ltems tser 'gro //
NG0423:4198: sprin bral nyi ma bzhin du rig pa lhag tser 'char //
NG0423:4199: shes rab spyan gyis phyir ltas snang ba'i yul ma bcings ma grol me long gzugs brnyan ltar //
NG0423:4200: snang la rang bzhin med par 'dzin pa bral //
NG0423:4201: shes rab spyan gyis nang du bltas pa'i tshe //
NG0423:4202: nyid kyis nyid bshad nyid kyis nyid la bshad //
NG0423:4203: nyid kyi ngo bor rtogs shing nyid kyis ngo bor grol //
NG0423:4204: spyi mdun nam mkha' mtha' la ye shes lam du bkrol //
NG0423:4205: gsang rdzogs phyag rgya chen po'i rang sa de //
NG0423:4206: de nas tshe 'di'am bar do nas ni //
NG0423:4208: grol ba sku gsum stobs che ba //
NG0423:4209: ye shes 'od zer dag tu mya ngan 'das //
NG0423:4210: 'gro ba sku gsum sa la grol bar nges //
NG0423:4211: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa'i rgyud nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:4212: skye ba brgyud nas grol ba'i le'u ste gya bdun pa'o ///
NG0423:4214: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / rab 'bring grol lugs ji ltar @#//
NG0423:4217: ye shes nyi zla kha sbyor las //
NG0423:4220: zhi gnas ye shes la brten nas //
NG0423:4221: rang shar lhag mthong 'char ba yin //
NG0423:4222: dran rtogs de la brten byas nas //
NG0423:4223: mi rtog ye shes mngon par 'char //
NG0423:4224: des snying po chos min blo las 'das //
NG0423:4226: mya ngan 'das pa mngon du thob //
NG0423:4228: dgongs pa dag la ma brten na //
NG0423:4229: mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob mi 'gyur //
NG0423:4230: tha ma grol lugs sku gsum lus rdzogs mthar //
NG0423:4231: mthong ba'i yul la rtags pa'i shes rab shar //
NG0423:4232: nga yi chos sku rnam dag la //
NG0423:4233: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes shar //
NG0423:4234: longs sku ma bskyed lhun gyis rdzogs //
NG0423:4235: chos sku rnam dag rang byung rtogs bral shar //
NG0423:4236: 'bring gi grol lugs bstan pa ni //
NG0423:4237: dang po phyi nang rtog pa 'gags //
NG0423:4238: gnyis pa rang gdangs ye shes snang ba 'od du gsal //
NG0423:4239: gsum pa de la skad cig gnas //
NG0423:4240: bzhi pa rang snang de la shes rab skyes //
NG0423:4241: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NG0423:4242: nam mkha'i mthongs nas nyi shar ltar //
NG0423:4243: rnam pa kun la mkhyen pa'i ye shes shar //
NG0423:4244: rab kyi grol lugs bstan pa ni //
NG0423:4245: skal ldan sprul pa'i sku yin pas //
NG0423:4247: skad cig drug la mya ngan 'das //
NG0423:4248: ye shes rlung gi stobs rnams kyis //
NG0423:4249: gzugs sku'i ngang la chos skur skyod //
NG0423:4250: tha ma gtso 'khor rim pas thim //
NG0423:4251: sprul sku 'byung lnga 'od lnga'i ngang du thim //
NG0423:4252: de lnga ye shes lnga yi ngang du grol //
NG0423:4253: dang po ma la shar bas ma yi ngang du zha //
NG0423:4254: chos nyid ngang la shar bas ngang du thim //
NG0423:4255: spyan gsum rnam dag 'gyur med gcig tu gsal //
NG0423:4257: chos nyid rig pa'i ye shes gnas //
NG0423:4258: phyi mi gsal ye shes nang gsal lo //
NG0423:4259: bum pa nang gi mar me gsal ba bzhin //
NG0423:4260: de tshe 'gyur med sku gsum rang sa zin //
NG0423:4261: rab ni sprul sku rdzogs ldan chen pos bya //
NG0423:4262: 'bras bu rdzogs sangs rgyas pa'i la dor ro //
NG0423:4263: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa las /
NG0423:4264: rab 'bring grol lugs kyi le'u ste gya brgyad pa'o ///
NG0423:4266: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / sku gsum rol pa'i mkhyen pa ji ltar lags //
NG0423:4267: mngon shes drug ldan spyan gsum 'char //
NG0423:4268: chos kyi spyan gyis yar la chos sku rin chen lta bur gzigs //
NG0423:4269: gzigs su med pa'i yul gzigs so //
NG0423:4270: thad kar longs sku tshom bu snang ba gzigs //
NG0423:4271: mar la sprul sku gnas lugs rtogs //
NG0423:4272: bag chags sbubs nas ji ltar gnas pa gzigs //
NG0423:4273: snyan gyi mngon shes yar la ni //
NG0423:4274: chos sku'i zhing na rtse gcig thugs kyi gleng ba gsan //
NG0423:4275: thad ka longs sku brda yis gsung yang gsan //
NG0423:4276: mar la sprul sku'i zhing khams na //
NG0423:4277: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra skad gsan //
NG0423:4278: thugs kyi mngon par shes pa yis //
NG0423:4279: yar la rin chen sbubs kyi chos sku //
NG0423:4281: shes rab 'dzin med rang gsal ba //
NG0423:4282: rang snang rtog med rig pa'i 'od gsal mkhyen //
NG0423:4283: thad ka tshom bu dgongs pa mi 'gag gsal //
NG0423:4284: mar la sems de rtog pa so so thams cad mkhyen //
NG0423:4285: gnas kyi mngon shes sku gsum bzhugs lugs ni //
NG0423:4286: chos sku chos dbyings longs sku 'od snang dang *//
NG0423:4287: sprul sku 'gro drug skye gnas mtho dman mkhyen //
NG0423:4288: las kyi mngon par shes pa ni //
NG0423:4289: sngon dang da lta phyis 'byung 'gro ba kun //
NG0423:4290: ji ltar spyod 'byung las 'bras rnam smin mkhyen //
NG0423:4291: spyan zhes pa yi brjod pa ni //
NG0423:4293: gsal ba mi rtog 'gro don mdzad //
NG0423:4294: thugs rje'i mngon par shes pa ni //
NG0423:4295: 'gro drug rang rang mthun pa ru //
NG0423:4296: sprul sku yul gzigs thub drug 'chad //
NG0423:4297: yi ge drug ldan sprul sku 'char //
NG0423:4298: ma sa sha a ha 'a dang drug / rigs kyi yi ge drug ces bya //
NG0423:4299: chos sku don du bzhugs pa las //
NG0423:4300: longs sku spyan las yi ge sprul par 'phro //
NG0423:4303: dkar dmar rnam gnyis lus bsgyur byas //
NG0423:4304: yi ge drug pos rig pa sems su brten //
NG0423:4306: lus kyi rgyu la sems kyi rten shar ba //
NG0423:4307: dkar dmar rig pa gnas pa ni //
NG0423:4308: gnas la gnas gab lus la sems kyi tshul //
NG0423:4309: des 'gro ba 'dren pa sprul sku mdzad //
NG0423:4310: 'gro ba ma lus thams cad la //
NG0423:4311: rang rig ye shes khyab gnas pas //
NG0423:4312: snying po 'gyur med ye shes 'gag pa med //
NG0423:4313: de don nges pa'i chos kun 'gro la ston //
NG0423:4314: thugs kyi dgongs pa 'gro ba kun la 'char //
NG0423:4315: ston pa'i dgongs pa longs gyur nas //
NG0423:4316: thugs la thugs 'dres bcud la bcud gab 'gyur //
NG0423:4317: de nas 'gro bas rtogs nas grol bar 'gyur //
NG0423:4318: zhes seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa las //
NG0423:4319: mkhyen tshad dang thugs rje 'byung tshul gyi le'u ste gya dgu pa'o ///
NG0423:4321: bcom ldan thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / thugs rje sprul sku mya ngan ji ltar 'da' //
NG0423:4323: de nas skad cig drug pa la //
NG0423:4324: ye shes rlung gi stobs ldan gyis //
NG0423:4325: dang po gzugs sku chos skur skyod //
NG0423:4326: de nas gtso 'khor rim par thim //
NG0423:4327: ye shes rlung gi chos nyid ngang la spyod //
NG0423:4328: de tshe 'byung ba mtshan ma rang sar grol //
NG0423:4329: sprul sku'i 'byung lnga 'od lnga'i ngang du thim //
NG0423:4330: 'od lnga ye shes lnga yi 'byung lngar grol //
NG0423:4331: dang po chos nyid ma la shar bas ma yi ngang du zhi //
NG0423:4332: stobs ldan ma dang shugs 'chang ma //
NG0423:4333: gnyis su med par sbyor bar byed //
NG0423:4334: dper na nyi ma'i snying po ltar //
NG0423:4335: rig pa'i rang rtsal sku dang ye shes shar //
NG0423:4336: tha ma 'khor rnams gtso la sdud //
NG0423:4337: gtso bo lnga yang chos sku rin chen sbubs su gshegs //
NG0423:4338: rtsol dang bcas nas bskyod pa ma yin te //
NG0423:4339: ngang gi 'gro ba phyir na shugs 'chang ngo *//
NG0423:4340: de dus chos sku rin chen lta bu ste //
NG0423:4341: gdos pa can gyi chos med de //
NG0423:4342: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu dang *//
NG0423:4343: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu gnyis //
NG0423:4344: gnyis med ye shes zang thal te //
NG0423:4346: sang nge gnas pas 'degs byed ma //
NG0423:4347: de tsam dus kyi ngo bo na //
NG0423:4348: rlung gis ye shes ma g.yos brtan mas bya'o //
NG0423:4349: de rnams mtshan nyid gcig la gnas pa'o //
NG0423:4350: 'byung ba ma la zha ba'i mtshan nyid lnga //
NG0423:4352: 'khrul pa'i sa chu me rlung lnga //
NG0423:4353: ye shes 'byung lnga'i ye shes gdangs la 'dus //
NG0423:4354: ye shes lnga yi 'od gdangs yang *//
NG0423:4356: de tshe rdo rje gya gram bkod legs gdan //
NG0423:4357: dus der g.yo ba med pa rgya gram ltar //
NG0423:4358: des ni g.yos pa med par bskyod pa'o //
NG0423:4360: chu shes 'khor lo brtsegs legs te //
NG0423:4362: gsher ba med pa'i chu zhes bya //
NG0423:4363: de nyid rnam dag dbyings nyid brtsegs legs so //
NG0423:4364: dbyings kyi rnam dag yan lag ni //
NG0423:4365: rig pa gsal stong dbyer med do //
NG0423:4366: de yi sa na ye shes spyan ma 'gags //
NG0423:4367: ye shes 'od gsal bum pa lngar shar ba //
NG0423:4368: de yi snying po rigs lnga gsal bkram brdal //
NG0423:4369: des na sra ba med pa'i sa brtsegs legs //
NG0423:4370: kye rigs kyi bu nges par zung *//
NG0423:4371: rang gsal 'dzin med sa nyid la //
NG0423:4372: sra ba med pa'i ngang du grol ba mi 'gyur ba //
NG0423:4374: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mchod rten ltar //
NG0423:4375: bzang ngan yangs dog che chung khong snyoms pas //
NG0423:4376: 'dug tshul sku yi ye shes las //
NG0423:4377: snang tshul sku yi shes rab shar //
NG0423:4378: rtogs pa gnyis med ye shes tshul //
NG0423:4379: 'byed pa med pa'i tshul shes so //
NG0423:4380: de yis dus nyid tsam na ni //
NG0423:4381: tsha bcas ma yang tsha med me yi ngang du grol //
NG0423:4382: rang rig ye shes gzhan snang rtog pa med //
NG0423:4383: dri med rig pa 'gyur med gnas //
NG0423:4384: me nyid pad+ma'i dra bas smin par byas //
NG0423:4385: rig pa 'thung lnga 'das pa'i rang gdangs la //
NG0423:4387: yid las 'das pa'i shes rab klong *//
NG0423:4388: nam mkha' khyab pa med pa'i gdangs can las //
NG0423:4389: skye 'gag nub pa med gnas pa //
NG0423:4390: rgyal mtshan rtse mo ltar du mthar bskyal lo //
NG0423:4391: de ltar 'byung lnga dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med shar //
NG0423:4392: de nyid de yi ngang du dag cing thim //
NG0423:4393: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las 'das shing *//
NG0423:4394: gzigs snang yul las 'das nas gnyis med pas //
NG0423:4395: ye shes rtse gcig ngang las gsal ba las //
NG0423:4396: ye shes spyan gyi ngo bo rnam par dag / de tshe shes rab spyan dang chos kyi spyan //
NG0423:4397: ye shes spyan gsum ngo bo dag nas gcig tu 'khyil //
NG0423:4398: kye rigs kyi bu nges par zung zhig / ye shes dbyings su thim pa yang *//
NG0423:4399: stong pa byang chad ma yin te //
NG0423:4400: chos dbyings ye shes thig le la //
NG0423:4401: gsher med chus med nang du bsdus //
NG0423:4402: sku dang ye shes nang gsal ngang du gnas //
NG0423:4403: shes rab mkha' la 'khyil ba zhes su bya //
NG0423:4404: rgyas par bstan na mtshan nyid bzhi //
NG0423:4405: sku dang ye shes dbyings thim nas //
NG0423:4406: rig pa rang gsal dbyings na ma 'gags pa //
NG0423:4407: ngo bo thim la ma rmugs pa zhes bya //
NG0423:4411: rang snang ye shes 'od gsal la 'das na //
NG0423:4412: gzhan snang rtog 'dzin mi mnga' dag / 'byed pa med pa'i shes rab 'gag med pas //
NG0423:4413: rig pa'i yon tan rang gi klong gsal ba //
NG0423:4414: yum gyi bum pa lnga na ye shes sku lnga gsal //
NG0423:4415: rang snang gzhan snang dag kyang ma 'dres so sor gsal //
NG0423:4416: rig pa'i rang sar gnas pa chos sku'i ngang *//
NG0423:4417: stong nyid rdo rje lta bu'i sku thob nas //
NG0423:4418: chos sku'i klong na ye shes longs sku ye shes spyan //
NG0423:4419: ma 'gags gsal bas sku gnyis rgyan du che //
NG0423:4420: g.yung drung lta bu tshe la ni //
NG0423:4422: thun med thun chen gcig gi ngang du grol //
NG0423:4423: rgyun gyi ting 'dzin rtse gcig ngang la gnas //
NG0423:4424: de tshe yul gnyis snang ba las grol nas //
NG0423:4425: rang snang gzhan snang rtog pa ngo bor dag /
NG0423:4426: sku gnyis 'das nas rin chen sbubs nyid gcer bur
NG0423:4427: gnas // spyan gnyis 'das nas ye shes rtse gcig go / shes rab mkha' la 'degs pa yis //
NG0423:4428: ma bskyod shugs kyis bskyod pa yin //
NG0423:4429: 'byung ba ma la zha ba yis //
NG0423:4430: mtshan ma rang sar grol bar byas //
NG0423:4431: ye shes dbyings su thim pa yis //
NG0423:4433: rtsal stobs bzhi la thim par ston //
NG0423:4434: shes rab mkha' la 'khyil ba yis //
NG0423:4435: sku gsum ye shes nang gsal lo //
NG0423:4436: rig pa rang sa zin pa yis //
NG0423:4437: dgongs pa 'gyur med mtha' ru skyol //
NG0423:4438: der sku gnyis chos skur mya ngan 'das //
NG0423:4439: mya ngan 'das pa'i ngo bo ni //
NG0423:4440: ngo bo mi gnas ye shes chen po yin //
NG0423:4441: nges tshig sdug bsngal mtha' las 'das pa ste //
NG0423:4442: mi rtog bde chen gnas pa'o //
NG0423:4443: dbye ba zag bcas mya ngan 'das //
NG0423:4446: mtshan nyid mtha' bzhi las grol 'das //
NG0423:4447: 'khor ba'i chos la mi gnas grol ba'i ngo bor shar //
NG0423:4448: grol ba rang ngo so so ste //
NG0423:4449: rang gdangs chen por gsal ba yin //
NG0423:4450: lus las grol ba'i ngo bo ni //
NG0423:4451: rtog med rig pa'i gnas lugs yin //
NG0423:4452: rig pa grol ba'i ngo bo ni //
NG0423:4453: rtsol ba'i chos las rab 'das shing *//
NG0423:4454: 'khrul pa gsum gyis ma bcings grol //
NG0423:4455: dper na sbrul mdud bor ba'am //
NG0423:4456: rnga ma dag pa'i mdud pa bzhin //
NG0423:4457: ngo bo nyid las ngo bor grol //
NG0423:4458: sku gnyis ye shes klong bskyod pa //
NG0423:4459: rdzogs sangs rgyas pa shes su bshad //
NG0423:4460: seng ge sgra nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:4461: sprul sku mya ngan 'da' bar bstan pa'i le'u ste dgu bcu pa'o ///
NG0423:4462: / gnas gsang chen dur khrod rol pa der //
NG0423:4463: me ri 'bar ba'i brag phug na //
NG0423:4464: gzhon du dpa' bo stobs ldan des //
NG0423:4465: lag na rdo rje nyer gnas byas //
NG0423:4466: rtse gsum mkha' 'gro rol mo dang *//
NG0423:4468: da ma ru yi sgra dbyangs dang *//
NG0423:4469: ka pa la yis zhal bu dang *//
NG0423:4470: bdud rtsi lnga dang sha lnga longs spyod dang *//
NG0423:4471: rus pa'i rgyan gyis mtshon nas ni //
NG0423:4474: byang chub sems dpa' rnam drug dang *//
NG0423:4477: mkha' 'gro pu rna nye bar zhi ba dang *//
NG0423:4478: mkha' 'gro tshangs pa dud mgrin ma dang *//
NG0423:4479: drang srong chen po zla 'od dang *//
NG0423:4480: khyung gi sder mo can dang bzhis //
NG0423:4481: de rnams yon bdag byas nas ni //
NG0423:4482: snang ba ston pa dam pa'i chos //
NG0423:4483: bdud rtsi yang zhun thigs pa 'di bshad do //
NG0423:4484: rgyud 'di ni seng ge sgra sgrogs dgongs pa theg
NG0423:4485: dman zil gyis gnon par yang zungs shig / ye
NG0423:4486: shes zung 'jug nyi zla kha sbyor zhes bya bar
NG0423:4487: yang zung */ ngo sprod ston nyi snang ba'i sgron mar yang zung */
NG0423:4488: sku gsum mngon rdzogs rgya rtag gser gyi me long
NG0423:4489: bya bar yang zungs shig ces rgyud gtad pa'i le'u
NG0423:4490: ste dgu bcu gcig pa'o // // mkha' 'gro rdo
NG0423:4492: nga rgyal rdo rje ma dang */
NG0423:4493: gti mug rdo rje ma dang */
NG0423:4495: phrag dogs rdo rje ma dang */
NG0423:4496: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor shugs can dang */
NG0423:4497: stobs kyi glang po dga' byed gzhon nu /
NG0423:4501: lag na rdo rje la sogs /
NG0423:4502: gser 'od dam pa sgra sgrogs pas thugs so sor tshim nas dga' mgu yi rangs te /
NG0423:4503: mgrin gcig tu thabs kyi rgyal pos yang gsang rgyud bshad pa /
NG0423:4505: sangs rgyas ma bkag ma sbyangs par //
NG0423:4506: ma btsal bde chen ngang la grol ba ngo mtshar ro //
NG0423:4507: 'di tshig kun la bshad pa'i thugs rje yis //
NG0423:4508: thabs mkhas thugs rje stobs mnga' byams pa khyod la 'dud //
NG0423:4509: e ma thugs rje thabs kyi bdag / snying po gsang ba don gyi rgyud gsungs pas //
NG0423:4510: snod kyi 'jig rten dbyings su dag / bcud kyi sems rtog ye shes rig par grol //
NG0423:4511: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsum ngo bor dag / dug lnga ye shes lngar shar nas //
NG0423:4512: bdag cag rnams kyang mi gnas ngang du mchi //
NG0423:4513: zhes mi rtog pa'i ngang du gshegs so //
NG0423:4514: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NG0423:4515: zhu ba po phyag na rdo rjes zhus /
NG0423:4516: dga' rab rdo rjes mjug bsdus so //
NG0423:4517: seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa nyi zla kha sbyor las /
NG0423:4518: rjes su yi rangs bstod pa'i le'u ste go gnyis pa'o ///
NG0423:4519: / pan+di ta bi ma la dang lo tsa ba
NG0423:4520: gnyags ku ma ras mchim phu bre'u dge'ur bsgyur cing
NG0423:4521: zhus te gtan la phab pa'i rgyud /
NG0423:4522: seng ge sgra'i dgongs pa nyi zla kha sbyor zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NG0423:4523: yang gsang rmad du byung ba bklags pas go ba'i bshad rgyud rdzogs so ///
